  salsaBachataBarcelona_intro:
    "At Farray's Center you don't just learn choreographies: you learn to dance for real. We teach Cuban Salsa, Bachata, Timba, Lady Style and Folklore from the roots, with musicality, technique and body awareness. With the exclusive Farray MethodÂ® created by Yunaisy Farray and Cuban teachers trained in Havana with international experience, we teach you to understand movement, master your style and dance with quality, presence and meaning. If you're looking to truly advance this is your place.",

