  afrocontemporaneoFaqQ1: 'What exactly is Afro Contemporary?',
  afrocontemporaneoFaqA1:
    'Afro Contemporary is a discipline created in Cuba at the National School of Art (ENA) that fuses universal modern dance techniques (Graham, LimÃ³n, Cunningham) with Cuban folklore (Yoruba rumba, Orishas, polyrhythm). It is considered the key discipline for comprehensive dancer development.',
